  <h1 class="page-title">about</h1>

  <article class="prose">
    <p>
      I'm Cyrus (<span lang="fa" dir="rtl">کوروس</span>, the name is
      Persian), a staff software engineer at Meta in New York, working
      on ads ranking AI.
    </p>
    <p>
      I specialize in ranking systems, recommender systems, and the
      infrastructure that makes applied ML reliable. Over the past decade,
      that has included recommenders at Dollar Shave Club, LLM fine-tuning
      at Google, the ML platform at HBO Max, and ranking models that serve
      billions of people at Meta.
    </p>
    <p>
      I also spent four years in engineering management, including two
      years leading a 15-engineer ads-ranking team at Meta. In May 2026,
      I returned to an individual-contributor role to focus on hands-on
      technical leadership: building systems, setting direction, and
      helping teams make better engineering decisions.
    </p>

