    <h2>off the clock</h2>
    <p>
      I build things that don't need a roadmap review: a computer
      vision pipeline that <a href="/work/nba-video-analysis">watches
      NBA games from broadcast video</a>, a
      <a href="/work/poe-league-tools">leveling copilot for Path of
      Exile</a>, and a rotating cast of LLM experiments.
    </p>
    <p>
      The common thread: systems that are honest about what they know.
      Models that abstain instead of guessing.
    </p>

